                        <interp inst="t18470920-name-795" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN ADCOCK</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I am sure the shoes were under my <hi rend="italic">bunk</hi>—that is not a place where I should leave them if I meant to give them up—the shoes and stockings produced are mine—the stockings were under my pillow.</p>
